Background
$l_{\mathbf{q}
u}^z$ can be written as
 egin{align} l_{\mathbf{q}
u}^z &= \sum_j  egin{bmatrix}  oldsymbol\epsilon_{j,\mathbf{q}
u}^{x*} \[6pt]  oldsymbol\epsilon_{j,\mathbf{q}
u}^{y*} \end{bmatrix} \cdot  egin{pmatrix} 0 & -i \ i\ & 0 \end{pmatrix} \cdot  egin{bmatrix}  oldsymbol\epsilon_{j,\mathbf{q}
